data.description: EXCELLENT AND CONVENIENT LOCATION! MUSTANG SCHOOLS! BUILT IN 2021! Welcome to a stunning 4 bed, 2 bath home with an open-concept layout. The covered front porch adds curb appeal and a spot for you to enjoy your morning coffee. The beautifully designed kitchen, with stainless steel appliances and nice pantry, is perfect for entertaining friends and family. A special feature to note is that the kitchen sink is built right in to your island--a wonderful use of space and allows for even easier clean up! The living room boasts canned lighting and an on-trend ceiling fan that everyone of your guests will be envious of. The inside utility area has room for storage and is located conveniently off the kitchen. The primary bedroom includes a a walk-in closet, raised ceiling, a ceiling fan, and two windows to let natural light in. The primary bathroom includes a custom tile shower, dual vanity and built in shelving. Bedrooms 2, 3 and 4 also have ceiling fans, carpet and a window for letting natural light in and the second bathroom also has storage shelving and a custom tile shower. When you add patio furniture, add a grill, and have time to enjoy the trampoline that stays with the house, your guests, children, pets, and family members will have plenty of space to take advantage of beautiful weather outside! The home has a tankless hot water heater, security system, and 2021 roof. The custom finishes and elegance throughout the home really elevates the space and is something that any owner would be proud of! (Buyer to verify lot Acreage/Land sqft. as not listed on tax records.)
